{"tid":1394060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美少女畫「豬頭人身」漫畫諷刺中國人是豬　涉「辱華」被捕　私密性感照全被起底","createTime":"2019-08-01T09:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T07:04:54.000Z","uid":14328,"like":105,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"afc668d90442f35af95a60b1f55af7f4766ae9bc","tid":1394060,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:47:01.000Z","msg":"內地近日一宗「以漫畫辱華」的案件引來大批網民關注，事緣一名22歲女生在微博發布多張「豬頭人身」諷刺漫畫，當地公安指該名女生為「精日分子」（精神日本人），其畫作侮辱中國人形象，嚴重傷害中華民族感情，踐踏民族尊嚴，對社會影響十分惡劣，故將她拘捕，案件正在審理當中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3098676/org/e485d15487d90152dee1d48b14c866f6.JPG/ygufdUQ4UTxAjMRxdYazb3ZYeK6Q1mmL2XpxP9l6cT8?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3098676%2Forg%2Fe485d15487d90152dee1d48b14c866f6.JPG%2FygufdUQ4UTxAjMRxdYazb3ZYeK6Q1mmL2XpxP9l6cT8%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=eb615e56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3098685/org/e67127af52650e4c2b3debbc7147ca5e.JPG/rVDs8Lv0iEFZmAv9ARBL-VYBbP0r4pHTj4vfj4-L348\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3098685%2Forg%2Fe67127af52650e4c2b3debbc7147ca5e.JPG%2FrVDs8Lv0iEFZmAv9ARBL-VYBbP0r4pHTj4vfj4-L348&h=10a5a273&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來自安徽省的22歲姓張少女曾以微博帳號「橘豚月月抽」分享自家創作漫畫，內容大多以諷刺社會事件為主，包括漢服流行現象、老兵討薪、中國遊客在泰國自助餐廳爭先恐後搶食等。（微博圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3098684/org/2a616b26b8eb0fb33af7ac4870f7c29c.JPG/sPCmGpnJZZbeu6BJmMmJOiCK_j_Be4Y5kIiucZCIrnE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3098684%2Forg%2F2a616b26b8eb0fb33af7ac4870f7c29c.JPG%2FsPCmGpnJZZbeu6BJmMmJOiCK_j_Be4Y5kIiucZCIrnE&h=b0f29f74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3098681/org/4e6c1d934bea72d36a7e926022963d82.JPG/e8SQ8zny8KcvLQb9Iy-n0fm1n1m0VCBhK953vCved7w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3098681%2Forg%2F4e6c1d934bea72d36a7e926022963d82.JPG%2Fe8SQ8zny8KcvLQb9Iy-n0fm1n1m0VCBhK953vCved7w&h=1a41dfc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3098679/org/dd7bb2b9bfbef73314935ef105ec7a35.JPG/hsvZWQEY8dRhB6Fj3-B1Uy7RIUQXloL1yx_218sf9tc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3098679%2Forg%2Fdd7bb2b9bfbef73314935ef105ec7a35.JPG%2FhsvZWQEY8dRhB6Fj3-B1Uy7RIUQXloL1yx_218sf9tc&h=6d644497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3098682/org/fe11e05ac5dd368cfc200b61a1b6d50b.jpg/hNKbDSYQO7ipDik7YC7I72LQ7AgI1ZEG_hmP3v4Zj94\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3098682%2Forg%2Ffe11e05ac5dd368cfc200b61a1b6d50b.jpg%2FhNKbDSYQO7ipDik7YC7I72LQ7AgI1ZEG_hmP3v4Zj94&h=4b7bcea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「精日」又稱「精神日本人」，是對精神上嚮往日本文化和歷史的一類人的貶稱，這類人通常還被認為盲目崇拜日本，甚至厭棄自己的中國人身份，罔顧歷史事實，竭力為日本侵略罪行辯解洗白。<br />\n<br />\n來自安徽省的22歲姓張姓女生曾以微博帳號「橘豚月月抽」分享自家創作漫畫，內容大多諷刺社會事件，包括漢服流行現象、老兵討薪、中國遊客在泰國自助餐廳爭先恐後搶食等，而畫作中除了外國人，內地人形象全是「豬頭人身」。<br />\n <br />\n安徽省淮南市公安局田家庵分局於28日晚發布通報，指「破獲一起境內外『精日』分子利用互聯網實施『辱華』違法犯罪活動案件」，並稱已批准逮捕該名少女。<br />\n<br />\n他們於通報中解釋，作品有辱華成份，是「侮辱中國人形象」、「刻意歪曲中國歷史事實，曲解國內外熱點新聞、事件，以諷刺、醜化中國人生活習慣」。<br />\n<br />\n通報又指該名少女「喜愛日本漫畫，極度崇拜日本文化，有明顯的『精日』反華傾向」。她曾於2017年9月在微博與另一名在日本的中國籍盧姓女子結識，並向盧女先後提供300多幅作品在網上發布。相關的微博帳號事後已被刪除，而盧女亦被遼寧省公安刑事拘留，案件現時正在進一步審理。<br />\n<br />\n（微博、搜狐新聞）<br />\n<br />\n事後該名少女慘被起底<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/01/y3l0Ps.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F01%2Fy3l0Ps.jpg&h=d48d806a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n私密照在不明渠道下全面曝光<br />\n<img src=\"https://zhina.wiki/images/thumb/0/0a/Zdn15.jpg/750px-Zdn15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzhina.wiki%2Fimages%2Fthumb%2F0%2F0a%2FZdn15.jpg%2F750px-Zdn15.jpg&h=365ed57f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國網民將其人格抹殺為騙財騙色的女子<br />\n<img src=\"https://zhina.wiki/images/thumb/4/48/Zdn39.jpg/375px-Zdn39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzhina.wiki%2Fimages%2Fthumb%2F4%2F48%2FZdn39.jpg%2F375px-Zdn39.jpg&h=4dc92117&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3663a0c6ca39b2843e577f0af40dff0258fc8a4","tid":1394060,"uid":172379,"like":48,"dislike":4,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:48:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c241d9cbabe2b9259298bcfa6c9588d3d0752219","tid":1394060,"uid":52230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:48:58.000Z","msg":"Cls"},{"pid":"6835116cf5e50697644542deea80c8dc91ccf5d9","tid":1394060,"uid":287028,"like":101,"dislike":4,"score":97,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:50:41.000Z","msg":"起人底真係好賤。 <br />\n<br />\n仲有冇多d圖?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6adb808320933d7abeca136124c02c1773dcf0a7","tid":1394060,"uid":117677,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:51:19.000Z","msg":"需要更多圖以作討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc9ec15390c7cf169ec6c7c220f866db72fdf82","tid":1394060,"uid":14328,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"6835116cf5e50697644542deea80c8dc91ccf5d9","tid":1394060,"uid":287028,"like":101,"dislike":4,"score":97,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:50:41.000Z","msg":"起人底真係好賤。 <br />\n<br />\n仲有冇多d圖?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:52:00.000Z","msg":"聽講流出出自中國大數據監控"},{"pid":"d2549c2c81b1b17083f7fdc51f7abdb6f71efdd6","tid":1394060,"uid":25858,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6835116cf5e50697644542deea80c8dc91ccf5d9","tid":1394060,"uid":287028,"like":101,"dislike":4,"score":97,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:50:41.000Z","msg":"起人底真係好賤。 <br />\n<br />\n仲有冇多d圖?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,